text: Sells a large variety of soya bean and cincau related drinks. Taste good. Ordered 1 soya bean drink ice cold at $1.30. highly recommended. This stall is tucked away behind the location, opposite the famous kway chap stall.
Loved my soybean grassjelly drink for $1.30. Good prices and everything is really fresh.
Nice and cheap soya bean and bean curd. Very thick and have a strong soya bean milk taste. They make their own soya milk and still selling for $1.20. üëç
Take away 2 soya bean curb. Price quite reasonable at $1.3 each soya bean curb.
Their Yuan yang drink was nice. üëçüèª
